Batelco Maintain Bid for Stake in Zain Saudi, Reuters Reports

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-03-19T09:45:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-19/batelco-maintain-bid-for-stake-in-zain-saudi-reuters-reports.html
Bahrain Telecommunications Co. will
move ahead with a joint $950 million cash offer for a stake in
Zain  Saudi Arabia  despite the end of the Kuwaiti firm’s $12
billion deal with Etisalat, Reuters reported, citing Batelco’s
chief executive Peter Kaliaropoulos.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  